{
  "texts": [
    "Although there is an improvement compared to employing single trading strategies, we have also identified certain limitations.",
    "These limitations are further addressed by other modules within the FinAgent system.",
    "Limitation 1: Gap in using multiple strategies to make a single decision In the role of a router, FinAgent demonstrates variable preferences for strategy decisions at each stage.",
    "This variability introduces a potential risk of unprofitable trading in such sequential decision-making scenarios, as each strategy operates based on unique assumptions.",
    "For instance, consider the period highlighted in Fig. 19."
  ]
}